          "color": "blue",
          "content": "麀"
        },
        {
          "type": "annotation",
          "source": "戚",
          "position": "",
          "color": "blue",
          "content": "，棚内两马相闹；小厮与家母饮酒，小姨与"
        },
        {
          "type": "annotation",
          "source": "戚",
          "position": "",
          "color": "blue",
          "content": "姐夫同床。可见有是主必有是奴，有是兄必有是弟，有是姐必有是妹，"
        },
        {
          "type": "annotation",
          "source": "戚",
          "position": "",
          "color": "blue",
          "content": "有是人必有是马。"
        }
      ]
